"title": "8151: revival, corporate",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8151: revival, corporate",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The experience of God's people both in the OT and NT when prayer is answered and their growth and effectiveness are renewed.</p>\n<h2>The recurring pattern of apostasy and revival in the OT</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:10-Judg2:19\">JDG 2:10–2:19</a></p>\n<h2>God is petitioned to revive his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:14-Ps80:15\">PSA 80:14–80:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:4-Ps85:7\">PSA 85:4–85:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:18\">JER 31:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:21\">LAM 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:2\">HAB 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Repentance is necessary for revival</h2>\n<h3>God's people are urged to repent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:6\">2CH 30:6</a></strong> <em>Hezekiah's appeal to all Israel.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1-Isa55:3\">ISA 55:1–55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">JER 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:40\">LAM 3:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:6\">HOS 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:2\">HOS 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:3\">ZEC 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:7\">MAL 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">REV 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:16\">REV 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:2-Rev3:3\">REV 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Wholehearted repentance is required</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12-Joel2:13\">JOL 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:29\">DEU 4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:2-Deut30:3\">DEU 30:2–30:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:13-Jer29:14\">JER 29:13–29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:18-Acts19:19\">ACT 19:18–19:19</a> <em>Repentance should be evidenced by deeds.</em></p>\n<h3>Repentance prepares for revival</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:20\">ISA 59:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:9-Judg10:16\">JDG 10:9–10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:1\">EZR 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:10-Ezra10:12\">EZR 10:10–10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:9\">NEH 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:30-Ezek18:32\">EZK 18:30–18:32</a></p>\n<h2>Revival is God's work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:2\">HOS 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:3\">PSA 80:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:7\">PSA 80:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:17-Ps80:19\">PSA 80:17–80:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:14-Isa32:17\">ISA 32:14–32:17</a></p>\n<h2>God promises revival</h2>\n<h3>God promises to revive his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19\">EZK 11:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">JER 31:33–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26\">EZK 36:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:6\">ZEC 10:6</a></p>\n<h3>The nations are included in the promise of revival</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3\">ISA 2:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2\">MIC 4:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:22-Isa19:25\">ISA 19:22–19:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:22\">ISA 45:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:6-Isa56:8\">ISA 56:6–56:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:20-Zech8:22\">ZEC 8:20–8:22</a></p>\n<h2>The revival of Israel</h2>\n<h3>Under Hezekiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4-2Kgs18:6\">2KI 18:4–18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:3-2Chr29:5\">2CH 29:3–29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:1\">2CH 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:4\">2CH 31:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:9-2Chr31:10\">2CH 31:9–31:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20-2Chr31:21\">2CH 31:20–31:21</a></p>\n<h3>Under Josiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:1-2Kgs23:4\">2KI 23:1–23:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:29-2Chr34:33\">2CH 34:29–34:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:1-2Chr35:3\">2CH 35:1–35:3</a></p>\n<h2>Revival in the NT</h2>\n<h3>Crowds turn to the Lord</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:5\">MRK 1:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:26\">JHN 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:39\">JHN 4:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41\">ACT 2:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:47\">ACT 2:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:4\">ACT 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:21\">ACT 11:21</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is active in the revival of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9\">ACT 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16\">2CO 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18\">EPH 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>The response of believers in revival</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:23-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:23–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:13–3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:14\">COL 3:9–3:14</a></p>",
